  "signal_description": "The query retrieves data from the table 'defaultview-217'. It calculates the number of cases for each variant and orders the results in descending order. The 'Number of Cases' column represents the count of cases for each variant. The 'Create => In Progress' column calculates the average time difference between the last 'Change Status to In Progress' event and the first 'Create Issue' event. The '%Create => In Progress' column calculates the percentage of the average time difference between 'Change Status to In Progress' and 'Create Issue' events, divided by the average time difference between 'Change Status to Closed' and 'Create Issue' events, multiplied by 100. The 'In Progress => Ready for Review' column calculates the average time difference between the last 'Change Status to Ready for Review' event and the first 'Change Status to In Progress' event. The 'Ready for Review => In Review' column calculates the average time difference between the last 'Change Status to In Review' event and the first 'Change Status to Ready for Review' event. The 'In Review => Closed' column calculates the average time difference between the last 'Change Status to Closed' event and the first 'Change Status to In Review' event."
